type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me think about this. The user is asking me to:\\n1. Check if today (March 30, 2026) is the last working day of this quarter\\n2. If yes, execute the quarterly daily report summary evaluation and scoring workflow\\n3. If no, reply with \\\"本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行\\\"\\n\\nFirst, let me determine what quarter today falls into:\\n- March 30, 2026 is a Monday\\n- Q1 = January, February, March (ending March 31)\\n- Today is March 30, which is the second-to-last day of Q1\\n\\nIs March 30, 2026 a working day? Let me check the calendar:\\n- March 30, 2026 is a Monday - this is a working day\\n- March 31, 2026 is a Tuesday - this is also a working day\\n\\nSo today (March 30) is NOT the last working day of Q1. The last working day would be March 31 (Tuesday).\\n\\nWait, I need to check if March 31 is a public holiday in China. Let me think... \\n\\nActually, I should just follow the instructions as given. Today is March 30, 2026 (Monday), which is NOT the last working day of Q1 (March 31 would be). So I should reply with \\\"本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行\\\".\\n\\nBut wait - this is a cron job asking me to perform the quarterly summary. The instructions say \\\"首先判断今天是否为本季度最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复'本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行'\\\"\\n\\n\\nSince today is indeed March 30, and the last working day of Q1 is March 31, today is not the last working day. I should respond with \\\"本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行\\\".\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"<final>本季度最后工作日不是今天，不执行</final>\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774802405045\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:2d1a4135-7087-496e-a6cf-d05365aa7fe8\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 运行系统持续优化\",\n    